snippet.title: PlayStation - Simple Character 2000 Series Vol 08 - Kagaku Ninja-Tai Gatchaman - The Shooting (2002)
snippet.description:
DESCRIPTION
The Shooting: Kagaku Ninja-Tai Gatchaman is an Action game, developed by Warashi and published by Bandai, which was released in Japan in 2002.
